				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Well it will definately be more interesting, I just think that one zone aside from bazaar should be non-pvp, just for lag sake if nothing else.  This is my only toon and I have been on Rallos for a little over two years, Xharlion, so I dont have any other frame of reference as to what is good for pvp and what is not, I only know Rallos as it is now. And although I am in an anti-pk guild, I do enjoy pvp.  However, I like being able to find groups and buffs without worrying about fighting.   You wont be able to /auc anymore, no more /afk in pok and, no more buffs behind bank...ack!
